      • add

        public boolean add(Element element)
        Adds an instance of Element to this shelf. If added, we will say that this contains element.

        The instance element will not be added to this if:

        • it is null;
        • it was previously added to a collection;
        • it was previously added to a shelf;
        • this already contains an instance that equals elementor
        • element has size 0 or occupies more space than the currently free space of this shelf.

        Specified by:
        add in interface Storage
        Parameters:
        element - The element to be added to this.
        Returns:
        true if the element was successfully added;
        false if the element was not added.

      • remove

        public boolean remove(Element element)
        Removes the instance element from this shelf.

        The instance element will not be removed from this if:

        • it is null;
        • it is not contained in this or
        • it is not available.

        Specified by:
        remove in interface Storage
        Parameters:
        element - The element to be removed from this.
        Returns:
        true if the element was successfully removed;
        false if the element was not removed.

      • requestElement

        public Element requestElement(Element element)
        Requests an instance that equals element from this shelf.

        The operation will not succeed if:

        • element is null;
        • no element of this equals element or
        • no element of this that equals element is available.

        Specified by:
        requestElement in interface RequestManager
        Parameters:
        element - The element to be removed from this.
        Returns:
        true if an element was successfully requested;
        false if the element was not requested.

      • returnElement

        public boolean returnElement(Element element)
        Returns the instance element to this shelf.

        The instance element will not be returned to this if:
